Synopsis: Removes an asset from a release on GitHub.
Description:
Removes an asset from a release on GitHub.

The Git repo for this module can be found here: http://aka.ms/PowerShellForGitHub
Inputs:
GitHub.Branch
GitHub.Content
GitHub.Event
GitHub.Issue
GitHub.IssueComment
GitHub.Label
GitHub.Milestone
GitHub.PullRequest
GitHub.Project
GitHub.ProjectCard
GitHub.ProjectColumn
GitHub.Release
GitHub.ReleaseAsset
GitHub.Repository

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 2
Examples.Code:
Remove-GitHubReleaseAsset -OwnerName microsoft -RepositoryName PowerShellForGitHub -Asset 1234567890 -Confirm:$false
Will not prompt for confirmation, as -Confirm:$false was specified.
